msgstr ""
"Project-Id-Version: Yakuza 6 Translation\n"
"Last-Translator: SavT\n"
"MIME-Version: 1.0\n"
"Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8\n"
"Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit\n"
"Language: it\n"

msgctxt "0||||4"
msgid "Gen-san went into the bar.\r\nMaybe I should drop by too."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "1||||4"
msgid "Welcome, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "2||||4"
msgid "Oh, Kiryu-san you came by!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "3||||4"
msgid "<symbol=note_with_outline> Kick on back <symbol=note_with_outline> Kiryu-san <symbol=note_with_outline>"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "4||||4"
msgid "Y-Yeah..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "5||||4"
msgid "What was that?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "6||||4"
msgid "Just my welcome-back-Kiryu-san song."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "7||||4"
msgid "If you're gonna break out into song,\r\nuse the new karaoke machine I bought."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "8||||4"
msgid "Karaoke, huh? About that...\r\nI got a bone t'pick with ya, Mama..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "9||||4"
msgid "Yer mad? Why?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "10||||4"
msgid "Because..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "11||||4"
msgid "(Hmm, I didn't add to the conversation\r\nand it ended awkwardly.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "12||||4"
msgid "(They're still in the bar. I should\r\nclear my head and get back in there.)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "13||||4"
msgid "Gen-san... You're an incredible singer.\r\nI'm pretty floored."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "14||||4"
msgid "You just realized that, Kiryu-san?\r\nI gots the best voice in town."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "15||||4"
msgid "It was super fun, though. All of my\r\nfavorite songs are on that machine."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "16||||4"
msgid "I'd need more throats to sing 'em all."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "17||||4"
msgid "Heh, I'm glad you enjoyed yourself.\r\nTechnology isn't so bad, right?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "18||||4"
msgid "Yer right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "19||||4"
msgid "Not that I can really talk.\r\nI don't keep up with tech either."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "20||||4"
msgid "Well, yer better off than me fer sure."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "21||||4"
msgid "I hate on gadgets 'cause it feels like\r\nI'm gettin' left behind in the past."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "22||||4"
msgid "But ya'll showed me jus' how wrong\r\nabout that I was."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "23||||4"
msgid "It was my own fear of change keepin'\r\nme stuck in the past."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "24||||4"
msgid "Then all you need to do is catch up.\r\nIt's never too late for that."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "25||||4"
msgid "I guess so... You're right."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "26||||4"
msgid "Maybe I'll start by buyin' one of those\r\nnewfangled smartphone thingies."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "27||||4"
msgid "They're all high tech and convenient, yeah?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "28||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I've got one myself,\r\nso I could give you a few tips."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "29||||4"
msgid "Really!? I'll be countin' on ya then,\r\nKiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "30||||4"
msgid "Well, no time like the present.\r\nI'm off to the store to buy one! See ya!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "31||||4"
msgid "Y-Yeah. See you later."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "32||||4"
msgid "Man, he's kind of impulsive."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "33||||4"
msgid "But I'm glad he's past his fear of using\r\nthat new karaoke machine."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "34||||4"
msgid "Hm? An email from Gen-san...\r\nDid he just send me a selfie!?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "35||||4"
msgid "Guess he already mastered his new phone.\r\nIf he's at the bar, maybe I'll drop by."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "36||||4"
msgid "Yo Kiryu-san, check it out!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "37||||4"
msgid "Hey Gen-san, looks like you're already\r\nusing your smartphone."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "38||||4"
msgid "Piece of cake!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "39||||4"
msgid "He's been playing with his new toy since\r\nhe got here. He's like a little kid."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "40||||4"
msgid "It's jus' so amazing. You can do\r\nanything with it. Right, Kiryu-san?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "41||||4"
msgid "Yeah, smartphones are convenient."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "42||||4"
msgid "The GPS can tell you the weather. It'll\r\neven navigate y'anywhere you wanna go!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "43||||4"
msgid "Wow, that is certainly convenient."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "44||||4"
msgid "(GPS...?)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "45||||4"
msgid "It can even stream high quality music.\r\nOh Kiryu-san, I wanted to ask something."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "46||||4"
msgid "Huh? S-Sure... What about?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "47||||4"
msgid "I'm gonna buy a Bluetooth headset to\r\nlisten to music. Any recommendations?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "48||||4"
msgid "(Blue... Tooth?)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "49||||4"
msgid "Ah, no... I don't know much about that yet..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "50||||4"
msgid "Darn. Well, lemme know if you find a good one.\r\nMan, the service is weak in the bar..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "51||||4"
msgid "Hey Mama, install some Wi-Fi in here!\r\nSpeed is king in the information age!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "52||||4"
msgid "(Wi... Fi?)"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "53||||4"
msgid "Yeah, yeah. I'll get to it.\r\nTalk about divin' in the deep end..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "54||||4"
msgid "Heh... Well I guess there's nothing\r\nleft for me to teach you..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "55||||4"
msgid "Not that I taught you anything\r\nto begin with..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "56||||4"
msgid "All right! Let's do some karaoke!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "57||||4"
msgid "Gen-san's gone wild!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "58||||4"
msgid "All right, I'm gonna sing a lot today. \r\nIt'll be a 12-hour duet with Mama!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "59||||4"
msgid "No way, I'd throw my voice out\r\nbefore I got halfway through that!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "60||||4"
msgid "Oh fine, fine. Let's start with\r\nmy jam, then... Today is a Diamond!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "61||||4"
msgid "Anyway... I'm glad Gen-san\r\ngot his love of karaoke back."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "62||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I was a little worried,\r\nbut that's passed now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "63||||4"
msgid "It can get quiet in here without\r\nGen-san singin'."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "64||||4"
msgid "Heh, it's a really lively bar."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "65||||4"
msgid "Oh, Kiryu-san!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "66||||4"
msgid "How's it going? You an expert at\r\nusing the karaoke machine yet?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "67||||4"
msgid "I've got it down completely! Started a\r\nmember account so it's even easier now."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "68||||4"
msgid "I'm kinda conflicted about him\r\nknowin' more about it than me now..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "69||||4"
msgid "Really? That's something."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "70||||4"
msgid "I haven't been gettin' as much exercise\r\nlately though, and it's affectin' my voice."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "71||||4"
msgid "Hmm, true. It doesn't seem t'carry\r\nquite like it used to."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "72||||4"
msgid "So, I wanted to talk to you Kiryu-san..."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "73||||4"
msgid "Hm? What about?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "74||||4"
msgid "You run a baseball team, right?\r\nGot room on the team fer me?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "75||||4"
msgid "You wanna join up?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "76||||4"
msgid "Yeah, I'll get my body movin' with some\r\nbaseball and take my voice back!"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "77||||4"
msgid "I've got confidence in my skills.\r\nHow 'bout it?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "78||||4"
msgid "I can see that. Of course we'll take you.\r\nI expect some big hits, Gen-san."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "79||||4"
msgid "You know it! Thanks.\r\nCan't wait to play ball with you, Kiryu-san."
msgstr ""

